Package: Rlldb
Title: R interface to LLDB for debugging code directly in R
Version: 0.1-0
Description: This package provides an interface to the LLDB
 API which allows us to run a debugger directly in R
 and to have callbacks to R to allow debugging commands to be 
 executed from R.
Author: Duncan Temple Lang
Maintainer: Duncan Temple Lang <duncan@r-project.org>
License: BSD_3_clause + file LICENSE
Imports: methods

